OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1774530671
OL,3,CWallsend school set for new building
OL,4,Cfollowing RAAC crisis
OL,6,FKris Jepson reports on the Wallsend
OL,7,Fschool selected to have a new state of
OL,8,Fthe art building following the RAAC
OL,9,Fcrisis.
OL,11,FA school in Wallsend is set to get a
OL,12,Fnew state of the art building,
OL,13,Ffollowing its temporary closure in
OL,14,F2023 due to structural problems with
OL,15,Fits roof.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/7
