OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1774530671
OL,3,CWallsend school set for new building
OL,4,Cfollowing RAAC crisis
OL,6,FA survey at St Columba's Catholic
OL,7,FPrimary School three years ago found
OL,8,Fthere were "major signs" of weakness
OL,9,Fin ceiling panels due to the presence
OL,10,Fof the "substandard material"
OL,11,Freinforced autoclaved aerated concrete
OL,12,F(RAAC).
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/7
