OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1774530671
OL,3,CWallsend school set for new building
OL,4,Cfollowing RAAC crisis
OL,6,FHeadteacher, Rachel Steinmetz,
OL,7,Fexplained how the crisis caused
OL,8,Fdisruption for pupils, saying: "We did
OL,9,Fhave to close the school the same day
OL,10,Fwe found out and we were split
OL,11,Foriginally between three different
OL,12,Fschools across the local area, for a
OL,13,Fwhile until this building was propped
OL,14,Fand made safe for us to come back."
OL,16,FThe pupils returned, with the roof
OL,17,Fpropped up by metal girders, the old
OL,18,Fbuilding was eventually closed
OL,19,Fpermanently, with the school moving
OL,20,Finto a temporary building onsite.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,423,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1774530671
OL,3,CWallsend school set for new building
OL,4,Cfollowing RAAC crisis
OL,6,FMrs Steinmetz added: "We've been
OL,7,Freally, really lucky to have the
OL,8,Ftemporary accommodation that we've
OL,9,Fhad. It's a bright, modern building
OL,10,Fand it's been great for us, sort of in
OL,11,Fthe interim. We've managed to keep our
OL,12,Fforest school area, we've managed to
OL,13,Fkeep all our lovely outdoor grounds
OL,14,Fand space and it's meant we've been
OL,15,Fable to really be back together as a
OL,16,Fschool community while waiting for a
OL,17,Fnew build."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
