FL,423,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1774530671
OL,3,CWallsend school set for new building
OL,4,Cfollowing RAAC crisis
OL,6,FThe wait for that new building is now
OL,7,Fover, with the government including
OL,8,Fthe school in its national rebuild
OL,9,Fprogramme.
OL,11,FIn Spring 2028, they will move into a
OL,12,Fbrand new school on site, which will
OL,13,Finclude Sport England standard playing
OL,14,Ffields, a solar panelled roof and
OL,15,Fstate of the art facilities.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
