PN,42206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1774530671
OL,3,CWallsend school set for new building
OL,4,Cfollowing RAAC crisis
OL,6,FDavid Douglass, the Deputy CEO of
OL,7,FBishop Berwick Catholic Education
OL,8,FTrust who run the school, said: "We
OL,9,Fhave a fantastic temporary building.
OL,10,FIn fact, most visitors don't realise
OL,11,Fthat it is temporary, but can you
OL,12,Fimagine by 2028 when we have a brand
OL,13,Fnew school, as we've said, with a
OL,14,Fsustainable roof, there reception area
OL,15,Fwill lead into a state of the art
OL,16,Flibrary, IT facilities, full sized
OL,17,Fsports hall, and classrooms that are
OL,18,Ffit for purpose and a brand new early
OL,19,Fyears section."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
